stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RESERVED: 設備初始狀態<br/>或註銷後
    
    RESERVED --> ACTIVE: activateSubscriber<br/>啟動設備
    
    ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED: suspend_subscriber<br/>暫停設備
    ACTIVE --> ACTIVE: update_subscriber_plan<br/>變更費率
    ACTIVE --> RESERVED: deactivate_subscriber<br/>註銷設備
    
    SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE: resume_subscriber<br/>恢復設備
    SUSPENDED --> RESERVED: deactivate_subscriber<br/>註銷設備
    
    RESERVED --> [*]: 設備可重新啟動
    
    note right of RESERVED
        ✅ 可執行操作:
        - activateSubscriber
        - validateDeviceString
        
        ❌ 不可執行:
        - update_subscriber_plan
        - suspend_subscriber
        - resume_subscriber
        - deactivate_subscriber
    end note
    
    note right of ACTIVE
        ✅ 可執行操作:
        - update_subscriber_plan
        - suspend_subscriber
        - deactivate_subscriber
        - accountSearch (有帳號)
        - validateDeviceString
        
        ❌ 不可執行:
        - activateSubscriber
        - resume_subscriber
    end note
    
    note right of SUSPENDED
        ✅ 可執行操作:
        - resume_subscriber
        - deactivate_subscriber
        - validateDeviceString
        
        ❌ 不可執行:
        - activateSubscriber
        - update_subscriber_plan
        - suspend_subscriber
    end note
